Katherine Nicole "Katie" Rees (born August 11, 1984) is an American former beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Nevad  a USA 2007
She was to compete in the Miss USA 2007 pageant, but was dethroned in December 2006 following the release of sexually charged pictures of her taken at a Florida nightclub three years prior.
Rees meriri aha Miss Nevada USA 2007 na izizi mbụ ya na asọmpi steeti emere na Las Vegas na Ọktoba 8, n'afo 2006
Ọ bụ Lauren Scyphers na-apụ apụ kpuchiri ya okpueze
"nwanne ya nwanyị", Miss Nevada Teen USA 2007, bụ Danielle Hashimoto.

Na Disemba 20, n'afọ 2006, e boro Rees ebubo na-egosipụta omume rụrụ arụ na ụlọ oriri na nkwari abalị nke Florida, afọ atọ tupu mgbe ọ na-anọghị na kọleji, e mere ọtụtụ foto nke Rees, isusu ụmụ nwanyị ndị ọzọ ọnụ, na ịme omume mmekọahụ ka ewepụtara ndị mgbasa ozi. Nke a sochiri mkparị metụtara Miss USA 2006 Tara Conner, nke akụkọ akụkọ kwuru na Conner na-aṅụ mmanya na-erubeghị afọ okwesiri iru, na-eji ọgwụ iwu na-akwadoghị na foto nke ya na-asusu Miss Teen USA ọnụ; E zigara Conner na rehab ma kwe ka ọ nọgide na-enwe aha ya.
N'abalị iri abụọ na otu n'ọnwa Disemba n'afọ 2006, ndị Miss Universe Organization wepụrụ Rees okpueze ya site na nkwado nke onye so nwe asọmupi
